snippet.title: LA-MULANA 1 & 2 - Launch Trailer (Nintendo Switch, PS4, XBox One)
snippet.description:
Out Now!
Find out more @ https://nisamerica.com/la-mulana-1-2/

Brandish thy whip and sharpen thy wit! LA-MULANA 1 & 2 marks the debut of two intense platforming classic on modern consoles for the first time ever. To claim the treasures within, you will need to prove your skills and your worth as you tackle trap-filled rooms, mind-bending puzzles, and the dangerous denizens of the ruins. Will you survive the trials and become a legend, or will you fail and be lost to time and history forever?

Available now on PS4, Nintendo Switch, and XBox One.
